    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Match New Sound Lengths\r\nUh oh! Kaysha needs to make these three sounds match up in her timeline. However, they are all different measure lengths.\r\n- `Main Beat` = 4 measures\r\n- `Piano Fill` = 3 measures\r\n- `Blip` = 1 measure \r\n\r\nUse `play together` and `loops` to make all sounds start and end at the same time. \r\n\r\n\r\nNeed help? Listen to the song in the media player. \r\n",
